```

## Conventions

- Schema in separate files by domain (`schema/users.ts`, `schema/posts.ts`)
- Snake_case for database column names
- `$defaultFn` for generated IDs (cuid2)
- Relations separated from schema for clarity
- Prepared statements for frequent queries
- Transactions for atomic operations
